  <summary date="2021-11-22T13:57:44Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Voters on the Move Registration Act of 2021 

This bill requires the Consumer Financial Protection Bureau to develop, and specified agencies to distribute, a statement providing individuals with information on how to register to vote and their voting rights. This information must be provided to individuals upon their participation in certain rental assistance programs or application for certain residential mortgages.</summary>
